/11/profit-Covid-lockdowns-750x471.png" data-large-file="https://flowingdata.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/profit-Covid-lockdowns-1090x685.png" /></a></p><p>在新冠疫情封锁期间，意大利电力公司收取了保费来弥补电费上涨，但这似乎还不是全部。 <a href="https://www.bloomberg.com/graphics/2023-italy-power-profits-covid-lockdown/?accessToken=eyJhbGciOiJIUzI1NiIsInR5cCI6IkpXVCJ9.eyJzb3VyY2UiOiJTdWJzY3JpYmVyR2lmdGVkQXJ0aWNsZSIsImlhdCI6MTY5OTk4NTEzMSwiZXhwIjoxNzAwNTg5OTMxLCJhcnRpY2xlSWQiOiJTM1ZTMVFEV1JHRzAwMSIsImJjb25uZWN0SWQiOiIzRDhGMEEzMTc2MDc0NUM5OTg4NkFCNzA1NDk2RUNEQSJ9.rm7Aj00wDrL3bW1amLCMmjeCb48Azu9BDdh0NppxkQM">Vernon Silver、Eric Fan 和 Sam Dodge 为 Bloomberg 分析了一段时间内的成本和保费</a>：</p><blockquote><p>即便如此，从高管们在财报电话会议上的庆祝言论以及简单的数学来看，很明显调度市场的较高价格帮助公司做得比仅仅避免损失要好得多。仅 2020 年，调度保费总额就达 12 亿欧元，比公司按日前价格计算的收入高出 238%。</p></blockquote><p>看来电力成本可能部分成为收取更多保费的借口。或许。不管怎样，我很喜欢日历热图上的发光美感。</p><p><strong>标签：</strong><a href="https://flowingdata.com/tag/bloomberg/" rel="tag">彭博社</a>、<a href="https://flowingdata.com/tag/covid/" rel="tag">新冠病毒</a>、<a href="https://flowingdata.com/tag/electricity/" rel="tag">电力</a>、<a href="https://flowingdata.com/tag/italy/" rel="tag">意大利</a></p>]]>;</content:encoded><post-id xmlns="com-wordpress:feed-additions:1"> 72679</post-id></item><item><title>索赔文件请求生成器</title><link/>https://flowingdata.com/2023/11/14/claim-file-request-generator/<dc:creator><![CDATA[Nathan Yau]]></dc:creator><pubDate> Tue, 14 Nov 2023 09:27:11 +0000</pubDate> <category><![CDATA[Infographics]]></category><category><![CDATA[claim]]></category><category><![CDATA[insurance]]></category><category><![CDATA[ProPublica]]></category><guid ispermalink="false"> https://flowingdata.com/?p=72659 </guid><description><![CDATA[<p> <a href="https://flowingdata.com/2023/11/14/claim-file-request-generator/"><img width="750" height="289" src="https://flowingdata.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/claim-file-generator-750x289.png" class="attachment-medium size-medium wp-post-image" alt="" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://flowingdata.com/wp-